@Node Introduction "Introduction"


  @{b}Introduction@{ub}


  Ever needed a quick way to do character conversions ASCII to EBCDIC and
  the other way round ? If so, then this little program will certainly
  help you.

  It convert a character or a file to its ASCII or EBCDIC counterpart.

  People using larger mainframes and mini computers probably have need
  for such a tool. XCOM, SNA and printing issues and code table problems
  can now be tackled without looking through translation tables.

  Just use CharConv !

          
@EndNode

